{"tid":1588161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]心理攻擊警犬有冇得諗?","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:16:09.000Z","uid":304726,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1317bd911ee44bb663b38565a799dd799bf9c73d","tid":1588161,"uid":304726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:40:48.000Z","msg":"眼見啲垃圾警犬咁自以為是，成日侮辱我地手足/FA。<br />\n其實對峙緊/圍警處個時係咪可以言語上侮辱返佢地呢班垃圾?至少口水戰打贏佢地，對佢地心理造成創傷。(由其是佢地四肢發達，頭腦簡單，心靈脆弱）<br />\n<br />\n例如:阿sir你係咪冇晒朋友呀孤兒仔?<br />\n         你老豆老母好後悔生咗你出黎呀!<br />\n         你個仔返學冇朋友比人杯葛呀!<br />\n         你老婆話你成日去叫雞想同你離婚呀!<br />\n         阿sir你冚家剷洗唔洗比錢你做帛金呀!<br />\n         阿sir得返啲低學歷人士支持你開唔開心呀?<br />\n         阿sir慘到要班福建佬/元朗黑社會支持你呀?<br />\n         阿sir你眾叛親離要上微博乞啲大陸人同情你呀?<br />\n         阿sir行出街夠唔夠膽抬頭，驚唔驚比人認出呀?<br />\n<br />\n利申冇讀過心理學，有冇巴絲有更惡毒嘅言語攻擊佢呢班社會渣滓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee2229e01f9b1be7168e2301df4f0dc73b10296","tid":1588161,"uid":293648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jyqfFZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjyqfFZE.png&h=963a252e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uxKfLQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuxKfLQq.png&h=1164f9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qVA6DMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqVA6DMs.png&h=c8dff230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ETMq24M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FETMq24M.png&h=d7900c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UFs72I4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUFs72I4.png&h=146fbb55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com